params.fastGasFeed: address of the Fast Gas price feed
params.linkEthFeed: address of the LINK/ETH price feed
params.paymentModel: the payment model of default, Arbitrum, or Optimism
params.registryGasOverhead: the gas overhead used by registry in performUpkeep

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

acceptOwnership().notice: Allows an ownership transfer to be completed by the recipient.

transferOwnership(address).notice: Allows an owner to begin transferring ownership to a new address, pending.

documentation.text:
@dev retrieves feed data for fast gas/eth and link/eth prices. if the feed
 data is stale it uses the configured fallback price. Once a price is picked
 for gas it takes the min of gas price in the transaction or the fast gas
 price in order to reduce costs for the upkeep clients.
@dev ensures all required checks are passed before an upkeep is performed
@dev ensures the upkeep is not cancelled and the caller is the upkeep admin
@dev generates a PerformParams struct for use in _performUpkeepWithParams()

@notice Base Keeper Registry contract, contains shared logic between
 KeeperRegistry and KeeperRegistryLogic
